Download the latest release:

 
 
curl -LO https://github.com/knadh/listmonk/releases/download/v3.0.0/listmonk-linux-amd64.tar.gz
tar -xzf listmonk-linux-amd64.tar.gz
cd listmonk
Generate and edit the configuration file:

 
 
./listmonk --new-config
nano config.toml
Setup the PostgreSQL Database:

 
 
./listmonk --install
Run the Application:

 
 
./listmonk
Access the Web Interface:

arduino
 
http://localhost:9000
